SubjectAdministrator of the Government of Ontario
PrecisAppointment to serve as ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of ONTARIO (1) the Hon. ROBERT J. SHARPE from January 27 to 29, 2015, inclusive; (2) the Hon. KATHRYN N.
